# 45. Final Architecture Summary

The Developer Intelligence Platform is built as a cloud-native, AI-assisted system with a modular architecture.

The architecture separates deterministic analysis (Rules Engine and Analytics Engine) from AI reasoning (Multi-Agent AI Layer), ensuring that recommendations are evidence-based, scalable, and explainable.

This design supports future expansion into enterprise recruitment, developer analytics, portfolio optimization, and AI-assisted engineering assessment without major architectural changes.